org.logevents.extend.servlets

Class LogEventFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.logevents.extend.servlets.LogEventFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Predicate<LogEvent>

    public class LogEventFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.function.Predicate<LogEvent>
    Queries a list of LogEvent objects by time, interval, threadName, logger, level, markers and mdcFilter.

    Use test(LogEvent) to filter a Stream of LogEvents and collectFacets(Collection) to return a summary of which threads, loggers, markers and mdcs were used in the interval.
